label: area_name
description: The official name of the geographic area.

label: area_type
description: The type of geographic area: California-Statewide, County, Metropolitan Area, Local Workforce Development Area, Sub-county places.

label: status
description: Current month data typically preliminary and is subject to revision, all others final and not subject to change.

label: employment
description: The proportion of the civilian non institutional population aged 16 years and over that is employed.

label: unemployment
description: Comprises all civilians 16 years and over who did not work during the survey week, who made specific efforts to find a job within the past four weeks, and who were available for work (except for temporary illness) during the survey week.

label: unemployment_rate
description: The unemployment rate represents the number unemployed as a percent of the labor force.
